<h1>Meet The Leadership Team</h1>  <hr /> <div style="background:#eee;border:1px solid #ccc;padding:5px 35px;"> <p>&nbsp;</p>  <p><strong><a href="/apps/_ee/files/rich-bane.jpg" rel="prettyPhoto"><img alt="BaneCare - Richard Bane, President" class="shadow" src="/apps/_ee/files/rich-bane.jpg" style="float: left; height: 317px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-right: 20px; width: 225px;" /></a><span style="font-size:18px"><span style="color:rgb(4, 82, 134)">Richard Bane, President</span></span></strong></p>  <p style="margin-left:.5in"><em>&ldquo;The world of long-term care is changing very quickly,&rdquo; says Richard Bane, president of BaneCare Management. &ldquo;We are not what people typically associate with a &lsquo;nursing home&rsquo;. Our facilities are technologically advanced and our staff is trained to handle complex medical situations. Our clinical expertise comes with a personal touch, because we truly care.&rdquo; </em></p>  <p>President Richard Bane and BaneCare continue to set the standard for premium skilled nursing care in Massachusetts.</p>  <p>A leading authority in the region&rsquo;s long-term care field, Bane lectures across the country and acts as chair of The Aurum Network, the largest post-acute network of independent skilled care providers in New England. A recent past chair of the Massachusetts Senior Care Association, Richard is a key decision maker for the entire Massachusetts skilled care community, leading efforts in Accountable Care.<br /> &nbsp;</p> </div>  <div> <div> <p>&nbsp;</p>  <div class="btgrid"> <div class="row row-1"> <div class="col col-md-4 col-xs-6"> <div class="content"> <div> <div class="shadow" style="overflow:hidden;height:180px;"><a href="/apps/_ee/files/harrison-bane.jpg" rel="prettyPhoto"><strong><img alt="Harrison Bane" src="/apps/_ee/files/harrison-bane.jpg" style="position:relative; top:-30px; width:100%" /></strong></a></div> </div>  <h4><strong><span style="color:#3399cc">Harrison Bane</span></strong></h4>  <p>Vice-President of Operations, BaneCare Management, LLC</p> </div> </div>  <div class="col col-md-4 col-xs-6"> <div class="content"> <div> <div class="shadow" style="overflow:hidden;height:180px;"><a href="/apps/_ee/files/andrew-bane.jpg" rel="prettyPhoto"><img alt="Andrew Gillis" src="/apps/_ee/files/andrew-bane.jpg" style="width:100%" /></a></div>  <h4><strong><span style="color:#3399cc">Andrew Gillis</span></strong></h4>  <p>Vice-President of Operations at BaneCare Management, LLC</p> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="col col-md-4 col-xs-6"> <div class="content"> <p>&nbsp;</p> </div> </div> </div> </div>  <p>&nbsp;</p> </div> </div> 